|  <strong class="text-white font-semibold">34</strong>  | <a href="../items/Box%20of%20Many%20Goods.md" class="text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 underline">Box of Many Goods</a>                     | Once per long rest, you can open this small box and roll a d12. On a result of 1–6, it’s empty. On a result of 7–10, it contains one random common consumable. On a result of 11–12, it contains two random common consumables.                                                                |
