|  <strong class="text-white font-semibold">40</strong>  | <a href="../items/Infinite%20Bag.md" class="text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 underline">Infinite Bag</a>                                   | When you store items in this bag, they are kept in a pocket dimension that never runs out of space. You can retrieve an item at any time.                                                                                                                                                      |
