|  <strong class="text-white font-semibold">51</strong>  | <a href="../items/Mythic%20Dust%20Recipe.md" class="text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 underline">Mythic Dust Recipe</a>                     | As a downtime move, you can use a handful of fine gold dust to craft Mythic Dust.                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|  <strong class="text-white font-semibold">52</strong>  | <a href="../items/Shard%20of%20Memory.md" class="text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 underline">Shard of Memory</a>                           | Once per long rest, you can spend 2 Hope to recall a domain card from your vault instead of paying its Recall Cost.                                                                                                                                                                            |
