|  <strong class="text-white font-semibold">56</strong>  | <a href="../items/Gem%20of%20Insight.md" class="text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 underline">Gem of Insight</a>                             | You can attach this gem to a weapon, allowing you to use your Instinct when making an attack with that weapon.                                                                                                                                                                                 |
