|  <strong class="text-white font-semibold">58</strong>  | <a href="../items/Gem%20of%20Sagacity.md" class="text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 underline">Gem of Sagacity</a>                           | You can attach this gem to a weapon, allowing you to use your Knowledge when making an attack with that weapon.                                                                                                                                                                                |
|  <strong class="text-white font-semibold">59</strong>  | <a href="../items/Ring%20of%20Unbreakable%20Resolve.md" class="text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 underline">Ring of Unbreakable Resolve</a> | Once per session, when the GM spends a Fear, you can spend 4 Hope to cancel the effects of that spent Fear.                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|  <strong class="text-white font-semibold">60</strong>  | <a href="../items/Belt%20of%20Unity.md" class="text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 underline">Belt of Unity</a>                               | Once per session, you can spend 5 Hope to lead a Tag Team Roll with three PCs instead of two.                                                                                                                                                                                                  |</p>
